{EAST has a balanced 23-point hand. He opens 2\C.

With 6 points and two 4-card Majors, WEST can only say 2\D.

EAST shows his minimum hand with a 2NT rebid.

Now WEST bids 3\C. This is not the second negative, but rather it is Stayman.

When EAST shows his \S suit WEST bids 4\S.}

