{When EAST opens 2\C WEST has enough strength (9 points) for a positive response. But, 
because her suit is \Ds, she must jump to 3\D.

EAST thinks slam and uses Blackwood to discover that WEST holds one Ace. 

That's all WEST needs to know to bid 6\D.}

